my first solo surgery.

41:14.446 --> 41:15.649
No way.

41:15.716 --> 41:18.421
That's amazing, Leela.

41:18.522 --> 41:20.024
Cheers to that.

41:26.838 --> 41:28.074
So how'd it go
with your patient?

41:28.140 --> 41:30.913
Just uncovered
a six-year-long misdiagnosis

41:30.979 --> 41:33.050
and started her on a treatment
to cure her cancer.

41:33.150 --> 41:34.252
So, no biggie.

41:34.319 --> 41:35.989
Wow.

41:36.591 --> 41:39.029
I think we're becoming
a power couple.

